  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Frei0r-plugins</title>

    <para><application>Frei0r</application> is a minimalistic plugin API for
    video effects. Note that the 0 in the name is a zero, not a capital letter
    o.</para>

    &lfs84_checked;

